nodes.cycle_function: Robot-1 Picks Tray from MHS
Robot-1 Places Tray on Conveyor
Robot-1 Goes Back to Home Position and Conveyors On
Robot-2 Picks Body 1 from Conveyor
Robot-2 Places Body 1 on local station
Robot-2 Picks Body 2 from Conveyor
Robot-2 Places Body 2 on local station
Robot-2 and Robot-3 Assemble Rocket Together
Conveyors move assembled rocket to Robot-4 and Robot-4 picks up tray
Robot-4 places tray on fixture
Robot-4 Disassembles Rocket's Nose
Robot-4 Disassembles Rocket Body 2
Robot-4 Disassembles Rocket Body 1
Robot-4 Disassembles Rocket's Tail
Robot-4 Places Rocket's Tail Back on Tray
Robot-4 Places Rocket's Nose Back on Tray
Robot-4 Places Rocket Body 1 Back on Tray
Robot-4 Places Rocket Body 2 Back on Tray
Robot-4 Picks Disassembled Tray
Robot-4 Places Tray on Material Handling Station(MHS)
Robot-4 Goes Back to Home Position
